<div id="dashboards" class="docs-section">
  <h2>Dashboards</h2>
  <p>Dashboards provide visual summaries of form activity and organizational data through embedded Power BI reports.</p>

  <h3>Accessing Dashboards</h3>
  <p>Click <strong>Dashboards</strong> in the profile dropdown. Available dashboards are displayed as cards. Click a dashboard to open it.</p>

  <h3>Interacting with Dashboards</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Use the built-in Power BI filters to drill into specific data.</li>
    <li>Dashboards refresh automatically with the latest data.</li>
    <li>Dashboard access may be limited based on your role and permissions.</li>
  </ul>
</div>
